  "prompt": "What is a good inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Power County ID?",
  "response": "While I cannot provide real-time information or specific recommendations, I can suggest some general steps to help you find a reputable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Power County, ID:\n\n1. **Online Search**: Use search engines to look for inpatient rehab centers in and around Power County. Keywords like \"inpatient drug rehab Power County ID\" or \"alcohol rehab centers near me\" can be helpful.\n\n2. **Local Resources**: Check with local health departments or community health organizations for recommendations on rehab facilities.\n\n3. **Referrals**: Seek referrals from healthcare providers, counselors, or community support groups who may have connections to rehab centers.\n\n4. **Insurance Provider**: If you have health insurance, contact your provider to find out which facilities are covered under your plan. They can also provide a list of authorized treatment centers.\n\n5. **Online Directories**: Websites like SAMHSA (Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration) have treatment locator tools. They can help you find certified rehab centers based on your location.\n\n6. **Reviews and Ratings**: Look for online reviews and patient testimonials to gauge the quality of care at various facilities.\n\n7. **Visits and Consultations**: If possible, visit a few centers or schedule consultations to ask questions about their programs, staff qualifications, and the types of therapies offered.\n\nMake sure to consider factors like the facility's accreditation, treatment approaches, staff-to-patient ratio, and aftercare support when evaluating options.",
